flowRoot.flowPara: For details or enquiries give us a shout (Michela: 07513709988, Roberto: 07595170750) or drop us an email at mich3la.esposito@gmail.com or roberto.torella@gmail.com.

Please confirm your intention to attend (or not) on or before 01 - 12 - 13. Any response received after this date will automatically enroll you in the washing up crew at the reception. So please, in your own interests, let us know by the 1st of December.
Please let us know if you have any dietary requirements. No, “two of everything” is not a dietary requirement.
Please dress comfortably : we will not have a Best Dress Prize. There might be a Best Costume Prize, though.

As you know, deciding to commit oneself to a lifelong, strict, binding contract can be stressful. So, after the ceremony, we will wash out the seriousness of the moment with a first round of drinks at Bar Spagnuolo, at a short walking distance from Palazzo Farnese, where the ceremony is held. If you attend the ceremony, you will be more than welcome to join us. No pain no gain, they say: don't cheat!
Please let us know the number of children accompanying you, we will arrange an alternative menu.
The option is also available for I-Don’t-Like-This-Either adults.

Any guest under the age of five, caught in the act of messing around, will be sold as slave. To help you keep constant the number of your progeny, a babysitting service will be provided. Also available for adults upon request.

The use of cameras or any other recording equipment, including mobile phones, is allowed and highly encouraged. The transmission or the distribution of any content, either in whole or in part or derivative works, in any media or medium, or any form, format, or on any social networking service now known or hereafter developed (yes, we are talking about Facebook) is prohibited unless such content would successfully qualify for publication in high profile magazines such as “Classic Tractor”, “Horse & Hound” and alike.

The recreational use of alcohol is allowed and indeed encouraged. If you too believe that water is just cause of shipwrecks and metal oxidation, please make sure there is someone who can drive you back home. We will spend the night at the Masseria.
As we will not enter the “Helmut Newton 2013” prize - category “Newlywed and Pigeons”, we can guarantee lunch beginning at lunchtime, as scheduled.
If you all are coming from the same place, why don’t you share a car? Car sharing is encouraged.
We remind you that the maximum number of passengers allowed per car is five, driver included, for the most common models. For more information please refer to your vehicle registration card.
